## Change 1 — NEW `api/analysis_templates.py`

Central registry of SQL templates. Each entry declares the template
ID, title, description, SQL (parameterized), parameter schema, and
row cap. All templates use `%s` placeholders; param values are passed
separately to psycopg `cursor.execute` which escapes safely.

